{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":77,"collapsed_counts":1,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560932852/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=28\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560932852/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=26\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":31},"data":[{"id":568689501,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568689501","content":"另外 你说自家人知道自家的难度\u003cbr\u003e这个初看尚可 细琢磨不到位\u003cbr\u003e首先，这个哥德巴赫猜想本身是数学问题，但是放在知乎上讨论则已经溢出了理科范畴，已经涉及了炒作 新闻 大众 精英 娱乐逻辑与学术逻辑等等文科范畴。\u003cbr\u003e所以，把哥德巴赫猜想放在这儿讨论，不可能只讨论哥德巴赫猜想，也会讨论作者，讨论知乎读者群，讨论哗众取宠，讨论价值观……\u003cbr\u003e这个问题，不是理科问题。\u003cbr\u003e而且另外，学过一点数学的，甚至学过历史的都知道这玩意基本证不了。\u003cbr\u003e我不知理工科学过多少哥德巴赫猜想 ，但每一个学过当代史的都知道毛爷爷奖励过陈景润，（那是基本没有科学的年代的奖励）知道徐迟给陈景润写的传记，文科生的确不了解哥德巴赫猜想，但学过这些，了解他的难度。\u003cbr\u003e我的回答还只是在文科的范畴内。\u003cbr\u003e希望你不要超出你的专业评论问题。\u003cbr\u003e希望你的统计有逻辑。你这份统计首先样本选择即有问题，其次，就算数据完全正确，也不能说明这份数据是由价值观所造成。我也可以这样统计，嫖娼被抓的多是理科生吸毒多是理科生，监狱高知多是理科生（因为理科生比文科生多 所以这些数据基本是可以确定的）所以这种统计并不能推出理科生价值观就差于文科生。\u003cbr\u003e我没学多少统计，但我知道你这个统计不对。假如你能证明这个统计是对的，那请你说服我。谢谢。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546343196,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"a4bf37137d25625f96170f808ed200aa","url_token":"bai-yang-he-xiao-xiao-54","name":"白杨何萧萧","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df30e548900b57cba7baf6d1c8ee7110_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df30e548900b57cba7baf6d1c8ee7110_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a4bf37137d25625f96170f808ed200aa","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":12,"child_comments":[{"id":568703115,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568703115","content":"唉…别激动…所以说自家人知道自家难度啊……你们只是从新闻报纸有个“难”的概念。但是理科学生，哪怕不是数学系，微积分概率论线性代数一般都是必修，这是切实学过，被虐过。就像法语大家都有个概念难，但是学法语的人才真的知道难。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e我其实看得出来很多文科生说着“我也知道不可能”，其实还是不清楚的。我说那句话，主要是这几天和很多鼓励题主的人争辩过(大概十几二十个吧)，往往点进去一看又是一个大学微积分不是必修的，记忆中几乎是没有遇到过理工科。而激烈反对题主的人里，理科生又占大半，文科生小半，倒也好像不是表达欲的问题。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e您说这种统计不完善我承认，那也许是我运气太好，小概率事件被我撞上了吧。而且部分鼓励题主的人不是“不知道哥德巴赫有多难”而是觉得“题主精神可嘉”，我气的主要是这个，题主精神不可嘉。而您觉得我在黑文科生不知道哥德巴赫猜想，其实不是的。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546345370,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"a4bf37137d25625f96170f808ed200aa","url_token":"bai-yang-he-xiao-xiao-54","name":"白杨何萧萧","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df30e548900b57cba7baf6d1c8ee7110_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df30e548900b57cba7baf6d1c8ee7110_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a4bf37137d25625f96170f808ed200aa","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":568714523,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/568714523","content":"我已经修改了答案，但是您怎么就不懂我要表达的东西呢？\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e绝大部分人都知道哥德巴赫猜想极难证明！\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e极少部分觉得哥猜有可能能被题主证明的，是你所纠结的“大众认知里哥猜很难”都没有达到的人群。你说文科生不能等同这部分人，我没有异议，我的重点也不在这部分真觉得高中生能证哥猜的人！\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e在“知道题主证不出”这个前提下，有一部分人的态度是，鼓励，题主有勇气挑战不可能！有一部分人的态度比如我是，反对，题主没有足够的知识储备就妄言解决，是对前人工作的践踏！\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e不管前一部分人是什么成分组成，我没有说他们大众认知上的哥猜难度都不知道，只是猜测他们鼓励的原因之一可能是对哥猜了解没有后者深刻，因此还觉得后者说的知识储备是有可能被跨越的。因此文科生有大众认知这点您不用给我翻来覆去地讲了好吗？","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546347137,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"a4bf37137d25625f96170f808ed200aa","url_token":"bai-yang-he-xiao-xiao-54","name":"白杨何萧萧","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df30e548900b57cba7baf6d1c8ee7110_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-df30e548900b57cba7baf6d1c8ee7110_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a4bf37137d25625f96170f808ed200aa","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0}]}]}
